&lt;li&gt;Plano de Saúde PET- Guapeco&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BYOD- Alugamos o seu notebook pessoal te pagando um valor mensal para que você o use, mas disponibilizamos também máquinas de trabalho para ílians. Você quem decide!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seu Niver, seu bolo!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seu Networking Vale Prêmio- Programa de premiação a indicação de novos funcionários.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mission:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Speechify is the most used text to speech reader app in the world with 25M+ users. We have voices like Mr. Beast and Snoop Dogg. Speechify stands at the forefront of Audio A.I. and voice cloning technologies, leading the industry with innovation and excellence. As Speechify continues its growth trajectory, our&amp;nbsp; executive team is actively seeking an Executive Assistant. If you&#39;re passionate about organization, adept at efficiently handling tasks, thrive in high-paced environments, and are eager to collaborate with a great team, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swiftly respond to customer concerns on written tickets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Google Calendar and email.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent reporting &amp;amp; response on every email and slack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent English reading and writing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and analytical skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to track and improve metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven customer support experience or experience as a client service representative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Touch typing 45 WPM and above&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong phone contact handling skills and active listening&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication (written and verbal), and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multi-task, prioritize, and manage time effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelors degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 6 months CS experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preference for applicants based in central and SE Asia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;A fast-growing environment where you can help shape the culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;An entrepreneurial crew that supports risk, intuition, and hustle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;A hands-off approach so you can focus and do your best work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;The opportunity to make an impact in a transformative industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-speechify-sentence=&quot;&quot;&gt;A competitive salary, a collegiate atmosphere, and a commitment to building a great asynchronous culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Think you’re a good fit for this job?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tell us more about yourself and why you&#39;re interested in the role when you apply. &lt;br&gt;And don’t forget to include links to your portfolio and LinkedIn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Not looking but know someone who would make a great fit?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Refer them!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speechify is committed to a diverse and inclusive workplace.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Speechify does not discriminate on the basis of race, national origin, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, protected veteran status, disability, age, or other legally protected status.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Gradle is the build tool of choice for millions of developers around the globe and is the official build tool for Android applications. Developing Gradle is a dynamic and demanding engineering challenge, with the reward of significant industry impact and collaboration with some of the world&#39;s best software teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our software is used by some of the world&#39;s leading software organizations, such as Netflix, Airbnb, Spotify, Twitter, and Atlassian. We regularly collaborate with these and other users to make our products continuously better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Profile&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Project Lead for Gradle Build Tool to help drive the evolution of the product to the next level and fully realize our vision, including developer-first software definition (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.gradle.org/declarative-gradle&quot;&gt;https://blog.gradle.org/declarative-gradle&lt;/a&gt;) and, in the future, broader polyglot support.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone deeply passionate about making other software engineers more productive who preferably has experience in a similar role in a major developer tooling product. The role is hands-on and requires a combination of technical depth, strategic thinking, and a product mindset.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The overarching primary responsibility is to help Gradle Build Tool advance its mission and achieve greater adoption and user satisfaction.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This involves:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guiding the technical and architectural direction of the project as a part of Gradle Build Tool leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being instrumental in defining, driving, and communicating the Gradle Build Tool product vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitating and fostering collaboration and effectiveness between sub-teams in service of the overall product vision.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Representing the project internally with key stakeholders and externally with strategic partners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fostering relationships with key influencers in the user community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with critical outreach efforts to clearly and effectively advocate for Gradle Build Tool.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gradle Build Tool leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be instrumental in Gradle Build Tool leadership, which currently consists of the VP of Engineering and platform/team leads.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help to build consensus and alignment in the Gradle Build Tool leadership team through productive collaboration, leveraging existing deep expertise, and integrating different perspectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Part of company leadership and broader impact on the business&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with key company stakeholders at a strategic level on Gradle Build Tool-related topics, especially with Develocity Engineering and Product, Marketing, and Developer Advocacy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with the Develocity project to identify and deliver value-increasing strategic initiatives in the service of both projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence Gradle Build Tool roadmap in a way that helps both the user community and the business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Representing the team externally&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the Gradle Build Tool team at a strategic level with key external partners such as Google, JetBrains, Spring, GitHub, and Microsoft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help to develop and maintain productive relationships in collaboration with the VP of Engineering and the rest of the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advocacy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shaping a more compelling narrative about our vision and deliverables, including mentoring the broader team on storytelling and directly contributing to strategic content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-on coding&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The role&#39;s primary focus is not to create software individually, but a degree of hands-on coding work is expected. Particularly, working with the codebase will be required to review critical engineering work and explore potential technical directions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
